Package: txtools
Title: An R package facilitating analysis of RNA modifications, structures, and interactions
Version: 1.0.5
Date: 2024-26-01
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miguel Angel",
           family = "Garcia-Campos",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "garciacampos.bioinfo@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5223-8174", 
                       webpage = "https://angelcampos.github.io/"))
Description: txtools is an R package that enables the processing, analysis, and
    visualization of RNA-seq data at the nucleotide-level resolution, seamlessly 
    integrating alignments to the genome with transcriptomic representation.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
